<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Auction Won!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .auction-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .winning-bid {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations! You Won! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{winnerName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Fantastic news! You have successfully won the auction and are now the highest bidder!</p>
        
        <div class="auction-details">
            <h3>Auction Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Item:</strong> {{auctionTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Auction ID:</strong> #{{auctionId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Seller:</strong> {{sellerName}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="winning-bid">
            Your Winning Bid: ${{winningBid}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>What happens next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>The seller will review your winning bid</li>
                <li>You'll receive a notification when the seller makes their decision</li>
                <li>If accepted, you'll receive transaction confirmation and invoice details</li>
                <li>The seller may also make a counter-offer, which you can accept or decline</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>Please keep an eye on your email and in-app notifications for updates from the seller.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for participating in our auction platform!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The AuctionBid Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from AuctionBid Platform</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
